v 3
d parqit — a grammar of data manipulation for Parquet on an embedded DuckDB engine
d Miguel Portela, Universidade do Minho & NIPE
d
d Reads, joins and manipulates columnar Parquet with ordinary Stata verbs that
d run out-of-core on an embedded DuckDB engine, materialising one result at a
d time into memory (parqit collect) or back to Parquet (parqit save).
d
p parqit  a grammar of data manipulation for Parquet (embedded DuckDB engine)
